\c 7
\s Ukukhululeka emlayweni
\p
\v 1 Kalazi yini, bazalwane (ngoba ngikhuluma lalabo abawaziyo umlayo), ukuthi umlayo ubusa umuntu selokhu esaphila?
\v 2 Ngoba umfazi\x + 1 Kor. 7.39.\x* owendileyo ubotshelwe ngomlayo endodeni ephilayo; kodwa uba indoda isifile, ukhululiwe emlayweni wendoda.
\v 3 Ngakho uba indoda isaphila, uzathiwa yisifebe uba esiba ngowenye indoda; kodwa uba indoda isifile, ukhululekile emlayweni, ukuze angabi yisifebe uba esiba ngowenye indoda\x + Mat. 5.32.\x*.
\v 4 Ngakho, bazalwane bami, selenziwe lafa lani emlayweni\x + 8.2. Gal. 5.18. Efe. 2.15. Kol. 2.14. Roma 6.2.\x* ngomzimba kaKristu\x + Efe. 2.16. Kol. 1.22.\x*, ukuze libe ngabomunye, ngabalowo owavuswa kwabafileyo, ukuze sithelele uNkulunkulu izithelo\x + Gal. 5.22. Efe. 5.9.\x*.
\v 5 Ngoba sathi sisenyameni, inkanuko zezono ezingomlayo zasebenza ezithweni zethu\x + 6.13.\x* ukuthelela\x + 1.20.\x* ukufa izithelo\x + 6.21.\x*.
\v 6 Kodwa khathesi-ke sesikhululiwe emthethweni, sifile mayelana lalokho esasibanjwe yikho, ukuze sikhonze ngobutsha bomoya, njalo kungeyisikho ngobudala bokulotshiweyo\x + 2 Kor. 3.6. Roma 2.27,29.\x*.
\s Umthetho lesono
\p
\v 7 Pho-ke sizakuthini? Umthetho uyisono yini? Phinde\x + 7.13. Luka 20.16.\x*! Kodwa bengingasazi isono, ngaphandle ngomthetho\x + 3.20. 4.15.\x*; ngoba bengingawazi umhawu futhi, uba umthetho ubungatshongo \add ukuthi\add*: Ungabi lomhawu\x + Eks. 20.17. Dute. 5.21. Roma 13.9.\x*.
\v 8 Kodwa isono, sizuze\x + 3.20. 4.15.\x* ithuba ngomthetho, sasebenza kimi umhawu wonke\x + 7.11. 2 Kor. 5.12. 11.12. Gal. 5.13. 1 Tim. 5.14.\x*; ngoba ngaphandle komlayo isono sifile\x + 3.28.\x*\x + 1 Kor. 15.56.\x*.
\v 9 Mina-ke ngake ngaphila ngaphandle komlayo\x + 3.28.\x*; kodwa kwathi sekufike umthetho, isono savuka\x + Luka 15.24,32. Roma 14.9. Isam. 20. 5.\x*, njalo ngafa mina;
\v 10 njalo umthetho ongowempilo, wona waficwa yimi ungowokufa\x + 10.5. 2 Kor. 3.7,9.\x*;
\v 11 ngoba isono, sizuze ithuba ngomthetho\x + 7.11. 2 Kor. 5.12. 11.12. Gal. 5.13. 1 Tim. 5.14.\x*, sangikhohlisa, sangibulala ngawo\x + Gen. 3.13.\x*.
\v 12 Ngakho umthetho ungcwele, lomlayo ungcwele\x + Hlab. 19.8.\x* njalo ulungile\x + Hlab. 119.137.\x*, futhi muhle\x + 7.16.\x*.
\v 13 Ngakho okulungileyo kwaba yikufa kimi yini? Phinde! Kodwa isono, ukuze sibonakaliswe ukuthi siyisono, sisebenza ukufa kimi ngokulungileyo; ukuze isono ngomthetho sibe yikonakala okukhulu kakhulu.
\p
\v 14 Ngoba siyazi ukuthi umthetho ungowomoya\x + 1 Kor. 3.1.\x*; kanti mina ngingowenyama\x + 1 Kor. 3.1.\x*, ngithengisiwe ngaphansi kwesono\x + 1 Kho. 21.20. Isa. 50.1. 52.3.\x*.
\v 15 Ngoba lokhu engikwenzayo, angivumelani\f + \fk angivumelani: \fl Gr. \fq angikwazi.\f* \add lakho\add*; ngoba kakusikho engikuthandayo, lokho engikwenzayo; kodwa lokho engikuzondayo, yikho engikwenzayo\x + Gal. 5.17. Roma 7.18,19.\x*.
\v 16 Uba ngisenza lokho engingakuthandiyo, ngiyawuvumela umthetho ukuthi ulungile\x + 1 Tim. 1.8. Roma 7.12.\x*.
\v 17 Kodwa khathesi-ke kakuseyimi engikwenzayo, kodwa yisono esihlala kimi\x + 7.20.\x*.
\v 18 Ngoba ngiyazi ukuthi kimi, lokhu kuyikuthi enyameni yami, kakuhlali okuhle\x + Gen. 6.5.\x*; ngoba kukhona ukuthanda kimi, kodwa ukwenza okuhle kangikutholi\x + Gal. 5.17. Roma 7.18,19.\x*.
\v 19 Ngoba okuhle engikuthandayo, kangikwenzi; kodwa okubi engingakuthandiyo, yikho engikwenzayo\x + Gal. 5.17. Roma 7.18,19.\x*.
\v 20 Kodwa uba ngisenza lokho mina engingakuthandiyo, kakuseyimi engikwenzayo, kodwa yisono esihlala kimi.
\v 21 Ngakho ngithola umthetho wokuthi lapho ngithanda ukwenza okuhle, okubi kukhona kimi\x + 7.20.\x*.
\v 22 Ngoba ngiyathokoza emthethweni kaNkulunkulu\x + Hlab. 119.35.\x* ngomuntu ophakathi\x + 2 Kor. 4.16. Efe. 3.16. 1 Pet. 3.4.\x*;
\v 23 kodwa ngibona ezithweni zami\x + 6.13.\x* omunye umthetho\x + Gal. 1.6.\x* olwa lomthetho wengqondo yami, longithumbela emthethweni wesono osezithweni zami\x + Gal. 5.17.\x*.
\v 24 Mina muntu olusizi! Ngubani ozangikhulula kulumzimba walokhukufa\x + 6.6. 8.23.\x*?
\v 25 Ngiyabonga uNkulunkulu ngoJesu Kristu iNkosi yethu. Ngalokho-ke mina ngokwami ngikhonza umthetho kaNkulunkulu ngengqondo, kodwa ngenyama umthetho wesono\x + 1 Kor. 15.57.\x*.